.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, lavender, aquamarine, turquise, ebony, apricot, purple
 1. the person who likes ebony is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Color   | lavender      | aquamarine   | turquise   | ebony      | white       | purple       | apricot     |

