.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, board-games, puzzles, sudoku, chess, rock-climbing
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the bartender is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is the photographer##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku     | board-games  | chess       | photography       | rock-climbing  | puzzles   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

