.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, folk, indie, jazz, metal, r&b, rock
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, november, july, october, august, january, february
 1. the fan of metal is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the fan of indie is the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the fan of folk##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | rock     | jazz     | indie      | folk | metal      | disco     |
| Birthday   | october | july | january | august | february | november | march |

