 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Hobby    | traveling | sudoku   | singing | hiking | magic-tricks  | camping | dancing |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

