.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, almond-milk, sprite, coffee, 7up, tea
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | tea | sprite | coffee | 7up     | lemonade | almond-milk |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

